OL,3,CSummerland survivor still searching
OL,4,Cfor mother's remains 51 years on
OL,6,FA survivor of the Summerland fire says
OL,7,Fshe is still searching for her
OL,8,Fmother's remains, 51 years after
OL,9,Flosing her in the disaster.
OL,11,FJackie Hallam was just 13 year's old
OL,12,Fwhen she was trapped at the centre of
OL,13,Fthe blaze.
OL,15,FShe was on holiday with her mum, Lorna
OL,16,FNorton and her best friend Jane Talon.
OL,18,FJackie was the only one of the group
OL,19,Fto make it out alive, and suffered
OL,20,Fterribly for years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
