OL,3,CSummerland survivor still searching
OL,4,Cfor mother's remains 51 years on
OL,6,FShe said: "I wanted to know what
OL,7,Fhappened to her final remains, because
OL,8,Fher ashes never came back to us.
OL,10,F"They were taken from the crematorium
OL,11,Fto a funeral director on the island,
OL,12,Fand then I've no idea what happened to
OL,13,Fher after that."
OL,15,FA total of 50 people died as a result
OL,16,Fof the Summerland fire, with many more
OL,17,Fsustaining injuries.
OL,19,FJackie's grandma travelled to the Isle
OL,20,Fof Man to identify Lorna, but this was
OL,21,Funsuccessful.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
