OL,3,CSummerland survivor still searching
OL,4,Cfor mother's remains 51 years on
OL,6,F"My grandma was asked to identify the
OL,7,Fcharred remains of someone, and she
OL,8,Fidentified someone who she thought
OL,9,Fmust be my mum, and this person came
OL,10,Fto Huddersfield.
OL,12,F"And it was discovered later that it
OL,13,Fwasn't her, and that poor family, I
OL,14,Fdon't know how they felt about their
OL,15,Floved one being toed-and-froed, but
OL,16,Fthat deceased person was returned to
OL,17,Fthe island".
OL,19,FJackie is campaigning to overturn the
OL,20,F'death by misadventure' verdict given
OL,21,Fto all those who died.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
