OL,3,CSummerland survivor still searching
OL,4,Cfor mother's remains 51 years on
OL,6,FThe 'Justice for Summerland' campaign
OL,7,Fgroup is formed of survivors, bereaved
OL,8,Ffamilies, and eyewitnesses of the fire.
OL,10,FThey are backed by lawyer Darragh
OL,11,FMackin, who recently overturned the
OL,12,FStardust nightclub verdicts in Dublin,
OL,13,FIreland.
OL,15,FAn application to reopen the inquest
OL,16,Finto Summerland is expected to be
OL,17,Fsubmitted soon.
